General.Name: Labyrinth Resources Limited
General.Description: Labyrinth Resources Limited operates as a gold development and exploration company in Australia. Its flagship property is the Labyrinth gold project located in the Abitibi Greenstone Belt region of Quebec, Canada. The company was formerly known as Orminex Limited and changed its name to Labyrinth Resources Limited in November 2021. Labyrinth Resources Limited was incorporated in 1970 and is based in Subiaco, Australia.
